							" Example DRV_HANDLE handle ; handle = DRV_SDMMC_Open ( DRV_SDMMC_INDEX_0  DRV_IO_INTENT_EXCLUSIVE ) ;  if  ( handle == DRV_HANDLE_INVALID )  {  // Unable to open the driver  } ",
